name: 10-25976-jbpt-bf54
notes: The surface water quality monitoring sampling conducted by Eastern Charlotte Waterways with the support of the Environmental Trust Fund in the outer Bay of Fundy Watershed in Southern New Brunswick collected data on surface water quality was designed to compliment data from existing federal DELG surface water quality sampling by conducting additional sampling at existing sites.

notes_translated.en: The surface water quality monitoring sampling conducted by Eastern Charlotte Waterways with the support of the Environmental Trust Fund in the outer Bay of Fundy Watershed in Southern New Brunswick collected data on surface water quality was designed to compliment data from existing federal DELG surface water quality sampling by conducting additional sampling at existing sites.
notes_translated.fr: L'échantillonnage de surveillance de la qualité des eaux de surface effectué par Eastern Charlotte Waterways avec le soutien du Fonds fiduciaire pour l'environnement dans le bassin versant de la baie de Fundy, dans le sud du Nouveau-Brunswick, a permis de recueillir des données sur la qualité des eaux de surface afin de compléter les données provenant de l'échantillonnage de la qualité des eaux de surface du DELG fédéral existant en effectuant des échantillonnages supplémentaires sur les sites existants.
